Package main.java.vlashchevskyi.exam.time

Provides classes that represent submission and booking time, allow to parse time records and compare objects by time.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseTime
    BaseTime is abstract class to represent booking request times.
    BaseTimeComparator
    BaseTimeComparator class is comparator to compare BaseTime objects
    BookingTime
    BookingTime class represents booking time record for booking request.
    SubmissionTime
    SubmissionTime class represents submission time record for booking request.
    TimeParser
    TimeParser class provides methods to parse booking request date and time including other information.
    WorkTime
    WorkTime class represents office working time.
